<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Chansons">Chansons</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Kazuo_Ishiguro&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=7" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" title="Modifier la section : Chansons">modifier</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Kazuo_Ishiguro&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Modifier la section : Chansons">modifier le code</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>Ishiguro a signé plusieurs textes pour la chanteuse de <a href="/wiki/Jazz" title="Jazz">jazz</a> américaine <a href="/wiki/Stacey_Kent" title="Stacey Kent">Stacey Kent</a>, pour ses albums <i><span class="lang-en" lang="en">Breakfast on The Morning Tram</span></i> (EMI, 2007) et <i><span class="lang-en" lang="en">The Changing Lights</span></i> (2013)
</p>
